== Overview ==
A higher powered version of the Talsian [[Plasma Cannon]] featuring an additional plasma chamber and extruded magnetic launcher.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Plasma Auto-Cannon can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Plasma Technology]].
